text: Leew Eilun Feer (Fering North Frisian for "Beloved Isle of Föhr") is the insular anthem of Föhr, in the Fering tongue. The lyrics were written by Knud Broder Knudsen (1864–1917).* ==Lyrics== ==References== * ==See also== *Üüs Söl’ring Lön’ Category:European anthems Category:North Frisian language Category:Regional songs Category:Föhr Category:German anthems
title: Leew Eilun Feer
